    "hero_title_gradient": "all-in-one, intelligent",
    "hero_subtitle": "Manask combines structured task management with Folder → Project → Task hierarchy, Pomodoro timer, AI chatbot, roadmap editor and detailed analytics — all in one web app, no installation needed.",
